Kennedy Nzechukwu kụrụ Carlos Ulberg n'asọmpị 'light heavyweight' UFC 259 iji nwete mbụgo.
Nke a mere dịka a na-atụ anya na Israel Adesanya ga-echịpịa Jan Blachowicz ọnụ n'ogo nke ha UFC 259 mana nke a emeghị.
Nzechukwu alụọla ọgụ UFC ugboro atọ ugbua , nke mbụ bụ ya na Paul Craig onye mba Scotland  kwatara ya, nke abụọ bụ ya na Darko Stosic na Newark, New Jersey .
Nke a o meriri Carlos Ulberg na Las Vegas bụ ọgụ atọ ya na UFC 259 kamgbe  ọnwa iri na asaa o kwụsịrị isonye n'ọgụ UFC maka ahụ o meruru.

Mmeri a tinyere oke ọnụ n'ọnụ ụmụ Naịjirịa dịka ha na-ekwu na ọ bụ eziokwu na Israel Adesanya emerighị n'asọmpị UFC 259 n'ogo nke ya na Jan Blachowicz kwatara mana mmeri Nzechukwu na-akasi ha obi ugbua.
Nzechukwu bụ nwa Imo steeti dị n'ala Naịjirịa.
A mụrụ ya n'ọnwa June 13,  n'afọ 1992.
Nzechukwu na ndị bee si Naịjirịa gawa nba Amerịka n'afọ 2010 dịka Wikipedia si depụta.
Nne ya mechara gaa debanye aha ya n'egwuregwu 'Mixed Martial Arts n'afọ 2015' mgbe ọ nọ na kọleji.
O mechara si n'ụlọakwụkwụ kọleji mgbe nne ya bidoro rịawa ọrịa.
Ihe Somadina kwuru maka Regina Daniels, ESN na Biafra7 Maachị 2021
